## Remarks  
  
> [!NOTE]
>  <span data-ttu-id="0ebd3-693">Le <xref:System.Xml.XmlValidatingReader> classe est obsolète dans [!INCLUDE[dnprdnext](~/includes/dnprdnext-md.md)].</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="0ebd3-693">The <xref:System.Xml.XmlValidatingReader> class is obsolete in [!INCLUDE[dnprdnext](~/includes/dnprdnext-md.md)].</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="0ebd3-694">Vous pouvez créer une validation <xref:System.Xml.XmlReader> instance à l’aide de la <xref:System.Xml.XmlReaderSettings> classe et le <xref:System.Xml.XmlReader.Create%2A> (méthode).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="0ebd3-694">You can create a validating <xref:System.Xml.XmlReader> instance by using the <xref:System.Xml.XmlReaderSettings> class and the <xref:System.Xml.XmlReader.Create%2A> method.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="0ebd3-695">Pour plus d'informations, consultez la section Notes de la page de référence <xref:System.Xml.XmlReader>.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="0ebd3-695">For more information, see the Remarks section of the <xref:System.Xml.XmlReader> reference page.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="0ebd3-696">L’utilisateur a besoin tester le type retourné.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="0ebd3-696">The user needs to test for the returned type.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="0ebd3-697">Par exemple :</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="0ebd3-697">For example,</span></span>  
  
```csharp  
object obj = vreader.SchemaType;  
 if (obj is XmlSchemaType)  
 {  
   XmlSchemaType st = (XmlSchemaType)obj;  
   // use XmlSchemaType object  
 }  
 if (obj is XmlSchemaDatatype)  
 {  
   XmlSchemaDatatype sd = (XmlSchemaDatatype)obj;  
   Type vt = sd.ValueType;  
   // use XmlSchemaDatatype object  
       }  
```  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="0ebd3-698">Si la validation de schéma XML est effectuée, le `XmlSchemaType` ou `XmlSchemaDatatype` correspond à l’élément actuel en cours de lecture.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="0ebd3-698">If XML Schema validation is being performed, the `XmlSchemaType` or `XmlSchemaDatatype` corresponds to the current element being read.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="0ebd3-699">Si la définition de type de document (validation DTD) est effectuée, cette propriété retourne `null`.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="0ebd3-699">If document type definition (DTD validation) is being performed, this property returns `null`.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="0ebd3-700">`XmlSchemaDatatype` est retourné si l’élément actuel, ou l’attribut est un type simple qui peut spécifier des contraintes de validation particulières sur les types simples, telles que min et max.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="0ebd3-700">`XmlSchemaDatatype` is returned if the current element, or attribute, is a simple type that can specify special validation constraints on the simple types, like min and max.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="0ebd3-701">`XmlSchemaSimpleType` est retourné si l’élément actuel, ou l’attribut est un simpleType défini par l’utilisateur.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="0ebd3-701">`XmlSchemaSimpleType` is returned if the current element, or attribute, is a user defined simpleType.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="0ebd3-702">`XmlSchemaComplexType` est retourné si l’élément actuel est un complexType défini par l’utilisateur.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="0ebd3-702">`XmlSchemaComplexType` is returned if the current element is a user defined complexType.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="0ebd3-703">Ce type ne peut pas être retourné par les attributs.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="0ebd3-703">This type cannot be returned by attributes.</span></span>  
  
> [!NOTE]
>  <span data-ttu-id="0ebd3-704">Si <xref:System.Xml.XmlValidatingReader.ValidationType%2A> a été défini ValidationType.None, aucune information de type de données n’est fournie à partir des schémas ou des DTD.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="0ebd3-704">If <xref:System.Xml.XmlValidatingReader.ValidationType%2A> has been set to ValidationType.None, no data type information is provided from either schemas or DTDs.</span></span>  
  
> [!CAUTION]
>  <span data-ttu-id="0ebd3-705">Après avoir appelé <xref:System.Xml.XmlValidatingReader.Close%2A>, SchemaType retourne Null.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="0ebd3-705">After calling <xref:System.Xml.XmlValidatingReader.Close%2A>, SchemaType will return Null.</span></span>  
  
   
  
